subject: RE: [junit] testing servlets  code
msgSnippet: Try also giving an explicit path to the java interpreter. I ve run into problems before when another java.exe existed earlier in the path. - George ... From:
messageBody:
Try also giving an explicit path to the java interpreter.
I've run into problems before when another java.exe existed
earlier in the path.

- George
